Ancestral Aspirant				KEY:Occultist Archetype ~ Ancestral Aspirant		CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.OccultistArchetype																							SOURCEPAGE:p.67		DESC:It is common for a noble to possess a deep pride for his family’s past, but when such self-importance gives way to obsession, an ancestral aspirant is born. Ancestral aspirants perform all the typical social functions of a noble, but they fill their conversations with stories of the great deeds of their family forebears, and they spend their nights researching old histories and primary sources, hungry for more.																					PRECLASS:1,Occultist=1		PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Occultist Archetype ~ Ancestral Aspirant],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Occultist_Archetype_ClassSkills=True,Occultist_Archetype_Implements=True,Occultist_Archetype_ObjectReading=True,Occultist_Archetype_OutsideContact=True]		ABILITY:Internal|AUTOMATIC|Ancestral Aspirant ~ Class Skills|PRECLASS:1,Occultist=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Ancestral Aspirant ~ Family Jewels|PRECLASS:1,Occultist=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Ancestral Aspirant ~ Emotional Reading|PRECLASS:1,Occultist=2	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Ancestral Aspirant ~ Courtly Contacts|PRECLASS:1,Occultist=8		FACT:Occultist_Archetype_ClassSkills|true	FACT:Occultist_Archetype_Implements|true	FACT:Occultist_Archetype_ObjectReading|true	FACT:Occultist_Archetype_OutsideContact|true	FACT:Occultist_CF_ClassSkills|true	FACT:Occultist_CF_ObjectReading|true	FACT:Occultist_CF_OutsideContact|true		COST:0
Secret Broker					KEY:Occultist Archetype ~ Secret Broker			CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.OccultistArchetype																							SOURCEPAGE:p.68		DESC:Whether as spymasters, extortionists, political fixers, or puppet masters, secret brokers use their talents with objects to gain information, then leverage that information for their own purposes.																																																									PRECLASS:1,Occultist=1		PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Occultist Archetype ~ Secret Broker],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Occultist_Archetype_ClassSkills=True,Occultist_Archetype_Implements=True,Occultist_Archetype_ImplementMastery=True,Occultist_Archetype_MagicItemSkill=True,Occultist_Archetype_ShiftFocus=True,Occultist_Archetype_MagicCircles=True,Occultist_Archetype_BindingCircles=True,Occultist_Archetype_FastCircles=True]		ABILITY:Internal|AUTOMATIC|Secret Broker ~ Class Skills|PRECLASS:1,Occultist=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Secret Broker ~ Knowledge Is Power|PRECLASS:1,Occultist=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Secret Broker ~ Broker Secrets|PRECLASS:1,Occultist=2	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Secret Broker ~ Share Memory|PRECLASS:1,Occultist=4	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Secret Broker ~ Steal Secret|PRECLASS:1,Occultist=8	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Secret Broker ~ Erase Secret|PRECLASS:1,Occultist=12	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Secret Broker ~ Purge Secret|PRECLASS:1,Occultist=16		FACT:Occultist_Archetype_ClassSkills|true	FACT:Occultist_Archetype_Implements|true	FACT:Occultist_Archetype_ImplementMastery|true	FACT:Occultist_Archetype_MagicItemSkill|true	FACT:Occultist_Archetype_ShiftFocus|true	FACT:Occultist_Archetype_MagicCircles|true	FACT:Occultist_Archetype_BindingCircles|true	FACT:Occultist_Archetype_FastCircles|true	FACT:Occultist_CF_MagicItemSkill|true	FACT:Occultist_CF_ShiftFocus|true	FACT:Occultist_CF_MagicCircles|true	FACT:Occultist_CF_BindingCircles|true	FACT:Occultist_CF_FastCircles|true		COST:0

